hjb.msg
Class MessageCopierFactory

java.lang.Object
  hjb.msg.MessageCopierFactory
public class MessageCopierFactory
extends Object

MessageCopierFactory determines the MessageCopier to be used to copy between specific instances of Messages and HJBMessages.

Author:
Tim Emiola
